            <li><b>76,234</b> tickets have been closed this year</li>
            <li><b>367</b> closed tickets have been reopened</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn" href="#">View details &raquo;</a></p>
      </div><!--/span-->
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="span7">
    <h2>Recent Activity</h2>
    <p>
      <dl class="dl-horizontal">
        <dt><span class="gray-sm">2h ago.</span></dt>
